7) Rod Woodson (soo fast)<br />
8 ) Stallworth (dependable, with deep play capability)<br />
9) Bettis (for years he faced 9 man fronts without passing attack, and still got job done)<br />
10) Plaxico Burress (we didn't have a real legit passing game until he arrived)</div>
			
